echanic of the ""-X-"" hints, when they're inside a cell or outside the board... {-0.5}- No ""Exit"" button. Most people don't really need it, but it still would've been nice to have.Total: +0.5... So close to not recommending. xDUpdate 2017-07-01: three of the dislikes i stated above are now somewhat addressed. Maybe they were from the start and i missed them, or maybe they were implemented in the mean time. But i still believe the level number (why is this NOT the x-y combo from the menu, but a counter not shown anywhere else?!), the Quit button, and the difference between perfected and completed-with-mistakes levels are WAY too faint to be really noticeable. :-s"
